abstract: Jesper Parnevik wins Insperity Invitational golf tournament; other golf news noted.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Golf; Swede Wins Champions Event

snippet: Jesper Parnevik of Sweden won the Insperity Invitational for his first Champions Tour victory, shooting a five-under-par 67 for a four-stroke victory in The Woodlands, Tex.
lead_paragraph: Jesper Parnevik of Sweden won the Insperity Invitational for his first Champions Tour victory, shooting a five-under-par 67 for a four-stroke victory in The Woodlands, Tex.
